    {
      "beat_id": "B13",
      "t_start": 108,
      "estimated_duration_s": 22,
      "narration_text": "Electron, mass 9.11\u00d710\u207b\u00b3\u00b9 kg, barrier height V\u2080 \u2212 E = 1 eV = 1.6\u00d710\u207b\u00b9\u2079 J. Decay constant \u03ba = \u221a(2m\u0394V)/\u0127 \u2248 5.1 nm\u207b\u00b9. Over 1 nm: probability density falls by e^{\u221210.2} \u2248 3.7\u00d710\u207b\u2075. Small \u2014 but measurable by an STM.",
